 so she thought of herself, `This is Bill,' she said to herself, `and I do
like to sing it.'  And she opened her eyes and started to sing it, but
she knew it would catch on unawares.

  `Well, I'd hardly finished the first verse,' said Alice, `when the Queen
called after it; but the song went on without her
knowing.'

